00:48:56,333 --> 00:48:58,083
Of course they dominate,

792
00:48:58,083 --> 00:49:00,959
on one side feel very happy that they are dominating.

793
00:49:01,750 --> 00:49:06,208
There was a lady who was boasting in one magazine

794
00:49:06,458 --> 00:49:09,041
that she has had four hundred men in her life.

795
00:49:09,041 --> 00:49:11,000
Can you imagine?

796
00:49:11,875 --> 00:49:14,999
Now there is no place for hell for such a woman even.

797
00:49:16,333 --> 00:49:18,792
Where will you put such a woman there?

798
00:49:19,542 --> 00:49:22,166
Now I don't know; that's another problem.

799
00:49:30,917 --> 00:49:33,667
So this movement,

800
00:49:34,542 --> 00:49:39,000
which is absolutely against the principle of dharma

801
00:49:39,625 --> 00:49:42,083
and of communication.

802
00:49:42,709 --> 00:49:46,000
Now how you must communicate

803
00:49:46,667 --> 00:49:48,834
decently,

804
00:49:49,250 --> 00:49:50,834
with very tender

805
00:49:52,834 --> 00:49:57,125
and very beautiful mannerism

806
00:49:57,458 --> 00:50:01,333
you have to talk to another person,

807
00:50:01,792 --> 00:50:04,083
talk to other Sahaja Yogis,

808
00:50:04,542 --> 00:50:06,250
talk to anyone,

809
00:50:07,000 --> 00:50:09,917
is in a very sweet manner you should talk.

810
00:50:09,917 --> 00:50:13,166
I do not mean the French style, you see,

811
00:50:13,166 --> 00:50:17,291
bending your body and all artificial stuff. Not that.

812
00:50:17,291 --> 00:50:22,375
I'm saying that if you are naturally talking to somebody,

813
00:50:23,625 --> 00:50:26,375
you should talk with decent language,

814
00:50:27,750 --> 00:50:31,500
with decency, with humility

815
00:50:32,917 --> 00:50:35,041
and need not go on jabbering all the time

816
00:50:35,041 --> 00:50:37,625
and talking too much. There's no need.

817
00:50:38,375 --> 00:50:40,250
But, on the contrary,

818
00:50:40,583 --> 00:50:42,959
this was the style was Shri Krishna.

819
00:50:43,166 --> 00:50:46,125
In short, His power was madhurya;

820
00:50:46,583 --> 00:50:49,500
is the sweetness, like the honey.

821
00:50:51,291 --> 00:50:54,959
When you are worshiping Shri Krishna

822
00:50:55,166 --> 00:50:57,834
you have to know that you must talk

823
00:50:58,166 --> 00:51:02,875
in a manner that will please another person.

824
00:51:20,041 --> 00:51:23,709
So, while talking to anyone

825
00:51:23,709 --> 00:51:26,125
you can talk very sweetly,

826
00:51:26,583 --> 00:51:31,625
very nicely and in a way which will please that person,

827
00:51:31,625 --> 00:51:33,125
not to provoke,

828
00:51:33,125 --> 00:51:35,709
not to say things which are hard.

829
00:51:36,166 --> 00:51:38,166
But some people have a habit

830
00:51:38,583 --> 00:51:43,250
of saying all the time something which is very provoking,

831
00:51:44,000 --> 00:51:46,583
which is not at all good.

832
00:51:47,834 --> 00:51:50,583
But some people are,

833
00:51:52,458 --> 00:51:56,166
when it comes to their business are very sweet,

834
00:51:57,125 --> 00:52:00,709
but when it comes to something else they are very harsh.

835
00:52:01,041 --> 00:52:03,750
We have a Jain community in India.

836
00:52:04,125 --> 00:52:05,750
I've seen many Jains.

837
00:52:06,250 --> 00:52:08,375
When they are for their business

838
00:52:08,625 --> 00:52:10,625
they're the sweetest you could know,

839
00:52:11,333 --> 00:52:16,959
but when it comes to something else

840
00:52:17,250 --> 00:52:20,125
like donating some money or something,

841
00:52:20,625 --> 00:52:22,959
they're extremely hard.

842
00:52:23,458 --> 00:52:26,125
They will only donate for stupid things,

843
00:52:26,500 --> 00:52:29,166
but not for something sensible.

844
00:52:29,917 --> 00:52:32,709
They'll work for something extremely stupid,

845
00:52:33,250 --> 00:52:35,834
but never for anything sensible.

846
00:52:35,834 --> 00:52:39,458
We have another community called as Sindhis.

847
00:52:39,458 --> 00:52:42,166
I think they are under the influence of the West.

848
00:52:42,542 --> 00:52:44,917
Same with the Western people.

849
00:52:45,542 --> 00:52:48,999
If you show that you have some business with them,

850
00:52:49,999 --> 00:52:52,166
suddenly you know, they change.

851
00:52:52,542 --> 00:52:54,875
Suddenly they change. You can't understand

852
00:52:55,083 --> 00:52:57,041
what has happened to this man.

853
00:52:57,750 --> 00:53:02,083
Or, if they find out you are something in life, they change.

854
00:53:02,417 --> 00:53:05,500
Shri Krishna was just the other way round.

855
00:53:05,999 --> 00:53:12,750
In His lifetime, He was always a guest of Vidhura

856
00:53:13,083 --> 00:53:20,458
who was the son of a Dhasi, is the servant.

857
00:53:20,458 --> 00:53:24,667
Maidservant's son was Vidhura, but he was a realized soul.

858
00:53:25,083 --> 00:53:28,208
So He used to go to his house,

859
00:53:28,625 --> 00:53:32,166
stay in his house, a very humble abode, Vidhura's,

860
00:53:32,542 --> 00:53:36,208
and eat food there, very simple food.

861
00:53:36,625 --> 00:53:40,500
But He would not go to the palace of Duryodhana.

862
00:53:42,208 --> 00:53:44,166
The other way round.

863
00:53:44,625 --> 00:53:47,291
I mean, somebody thinks that you have a palace,

864
00:53:47,625 --> 00:53:50,750
they'll be extremely kind to you, very nice, you know.

865
00:53:51,417 --> 00:53:54,542
But they say he lives in a hut, then he's nothing.

866
00:53:56,750 --> 00:53:59,542
It's such a money orientation in subtle way.

867
00:54:00,750 --> 00:54:03,917
Shri Krishna never, never cared for money

868
00:54:04,417 --> 00:54:06,750
and never bothered about it.

869
00:54:07,625 --> 00:54:10,083
You can see His case

870
00:54:10,750 --> 00:54:15,750
in which He has shown complete detachment

871
00:54:16,083 --> 00:54:20,208
about His throne, or His kingdom,

872
00:54:20,750 --> 00:54:23,667
or money part of it.

873
00:54:24,333 --> 00:54:28,500
Once you are attached you have all the pangs of money.

874
00:54:29,041 --> 00:54:31,291
Naturally, if you are catching hold of a snake

875
00:54:31,542 --> 00:54:35,542
you'll always be having the pangs of the snake, don't you?

876
00:54:35,792 --> 00:54:38,083
But supposing you are detached.

877
00:54:38,917 --> 00:54:41,875
Then the same money you can use.

878
00:54:43,333 --> 00:54:45,999
Once you become slave of that money,

879
00:54:46,291 --> 00:54:48,792
that money sits on your head.

880
00:54:50,208 --> 00:54:53,999
Now, you know very well that to have money

881
00:54:54,208 --> 00:54:56,417
also is dangerous these days.

882
00:54:57,999 --> 00:55:00,417
The whole reaction is building up

883
00:55:00,750 --> 00:55:02,959
and this is where the whole

884
00:55:03,166 --> 00:55:06,166
all the elements are reacting against you.

885
00:55:07,417 --> 00:55:11,417
You have seen the wisdom of these people from Sierra Nevada,

886
00:55:11,792 --> 00:55:13,792
and what they said is true

887
00:55:14,417 --> 00:55:23,083
that when we try to acquire more money,

888
00:55:24,000 --> 00:55:26,417
go on acquiring, go on acquiring

889
00:55:27,417 --> 00:55:31,333
and getting a idea in our head,

890
00:55:32,917 --> 00:55:35,999
then there are looters who come round.

891
00:55:36,208 --> 00:55:38,125
I think the worst are those

892
00:55:38,417 --> 00:55:42,417
who have got names as entrepreneurs.

893
00:55:42,792 --> 00:55:44,999
For example, they'll say, "Now,

894
00:55:45,208 --> 00:55:48,917
if you have a designer's watch",

895
00:55:53,083 --> 00:55:56,417
then everybody ran for designer's watches.

896
00:55:58,417 --> 00:56:03,542
The other day I went to Italy, no, to Istanbul

897
00:56:03,875 --> 00:56:07,208
and I found out that the T-shirts are made there

898
00:56:07,542 --> 00:56:10,583
and sold in France as if they are French. They are not.

899
00:56:10,917 --> 00:56:17,667
They are A to Z, they are made in there, which is Istanbul

900
00:56:18,208 --> 00:56:20,917
and the name is on that Lacoste,

901
00:56:21,125 --> 00:56:23,000
this that and all that.

902
00:56:23,333 --> 00:56:26,083
And people pay any amount, but not in Turkey.

903
00:56:26,333 --> 00:56:31,208
Whatever surplus is left we can get it for seven pounds.

904
00:56:32,542 --> 00:56:36,542
Now the stupidity is that they can befool you.

905
00:56:38,667 --> 00:56:41,667
Pierre Cardin, then there's another one,

906
00:56:42,125 --> 00:56:45,917
I don't know, Armani - that's in Italy only,

907
00:56:46,125 --> 00:56:48,458
but in America there are many.

908
00:56:48,709 --> 00:56:51,458
Even, I mean, they come to you,

909
00:56:51,709 --> 00:56:52,834
to your house.

910
00:56:52,834 --> 00:56:54,583
England is much worse.

911
00:56:54,917 --> 00:56:56,250
They're so unmannerly,

912
00:56:56,542 --> 00:56:58,375
they'll come to your house for dinner

913
00:56:58,792 --> 00:57:02,375
and they'll turn the plate to see where it is made.

914
00:57:03,417 --> 00:57:05,375
Really. Openly.

915
00:57:05,834 --> 00:57:09,667
And they'll discuss from where the cutlery has come.

916
00:57:13,083 --> 00:57:16,583
So, though they think they're very rich,

917
00:57:16,583 --> 00:57:20,458
stupidly they are being exploited by this kind of a nonsense

918
00:57:21,250 --> 00:57:24,542
that you have this watch, you have this thing.

919
00:57:24,917 --> 00:57:28,458
Now, in England we have something called Saville Row,

920
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:31,834
so that they put it outside, you know,

921
00:57:31,834 --> 00:57:34,542
outside the coat - Saville Row.

922
00:57:34,542 --> 00:57:36,583
Can you imagine?

923
00:57:36,834 --> 00:57:38,458
Branded.

924
00:57:38,917 --> 00:57:43,333
See, everything is made into a big ado.

925
00:57:43,792 --> 00:57:45,999
So on one side they are very intelligent

926
00:57:46,208 --> 00:57:48,375
to understand this is the business,

927
00:57:48,375 --> 00:57:52,000
this is the fashion all that.

928
00:57:52,333 --> 00:57:55,083
The other side they don't know they are fools,

929
00:57:55,583 --> 00:57:57,792
being befooled all the time by saying

930
00:57:58,000 --> 00:58:01,000
this is the special thing, that is the special thing

931
00:58:01,375 --> 00:58:05,125
and that it has a name and it has, what you call,

932
00:58:05,542 --> 00:58:09,667
the - a great organization behind it.

933
00:58:12,250 --> 00:58:15,458
Sahaja Yogis should understand this is all befooling

934
00:58:15,917 --> 00:58:19,250
and stupid thing and they wear,

935
00:58:19,542 --> 00:58:21,999
all of them will wear like that just to show off.

936
00:58:23,333 --> 00:58:24,583
What is it?

937
00:58:24,583 --> 00:58:28,333
Why should this impress anyone?

938
00:58:28,917 --> 00:58:30,709
Think of it.

939
00:58:31,083 --> 00:58:34,834
Now, intelligently think why should it impress you,

940
00:58:35,375 --> 00:58:37,917
these befooling things that are going on?

941
00:58:38,125 --> 00:58:39,125
Nothing special.

942
00:58:39,125 --> 00:58:41,458
They are just the same.

943
00:58:41,792 --> 00:58:46,208
They told Me in Istanbul that they make ordinary ones

944
00:58:46,458 --> 00:58:48,792
and then they put on top of this mark

945
00:58:49,083 --> 00:58:52,458
and the ordinary ones are for, say,

946
00:58:52,709 --> 00:58:56,583
six dollars, so with this thing is for seven dollars.

947
00:58:58,917 --> 00:59:00,999
There's nothing special,

948
00:59:02,125 --> 00:59:06,125
but this special trickery, I think,

949
00:59:06,125 --> 00:59:10,583
is coming from England and America especially

950
00:59:11,250 --> 00:59:15,709
maybe also from France, but France are, you know,

951
00:59:15,709 --> 00:59:17,208
queer people.

952
00:59:17,667 --> 00:59:20,792
Now they have something. I showed them today -

953
00:59:21,208 --> 00:59:24,458
So stupidly made thing,

954
00:59:24,792 --> 00:59:27,917
which cost five hundred pounds,

955
00:59:28,375 --> 00:59:32,250
but people accept because they have no wisdom.

956
00:59:32,834 --> 00:59:37,333
Now see the difference between the intelligence and wisdom.

957
00:59:39,083 --> 00:59:41,709
Why to show off, first of all

958
00:59:42,000 --> 00:59:44,542
and to show off something which has no meaning?

959
00:59:44,834 --> 00:59:51,542
It cost only one dollar in Turkey to put that thing on

960
00:59:51,542 --> 00:59:54,583
and stupidly people are showing it.

961
00:59:58,792 --> 01:00:04,125
Is it that we have intelligence,

962
01:00:05,208 --> 01:00:07,458
but which has no divine power?

963
01:00:07,792 --> 01:00:11,333
Anybody can befool you to do what you like.

964
01:00:11,709 --> 01:00:13,709
Now six inches of skirt started.

965
01:00:13,709 --> 01:00:15,542
All right, everywhere six inches.

966
01:00:15,792 --> 01:00:18,667
You couldn't get one with the seven inches even.

967
01:00:19,333 --> 01:00:21,000
That's not in the fashion.

968
01:00:21,250 --> 01:00:24,208
That's not in - means 'in' in madhouse?

969
01:00:27,208 --> 01:00:31,709
Now just look at Shri Krishna's style - so wise,

970
01:00:32,583 --> 01:00:34,333
witnessing everything,

971
01:00:34,667 --> 01:00:36,709
how He plays around

972
01:00:38,417 --> 01:00:40,458
and how He wins over.

973
01:00:41,333 --> 01:00:43,583
Now, supposing He was attached.

974
01:00:43,583 --> 01:00:46,333
He could not have done it.

975
01:00:48,083 --> 01:00:51,917
So to get over this, first of all, you detach yourself from this

976
01:00:52,208 --> 01:00:54,999
anti-Shri Krishna culture.

977
01:00:54,999 --> 01:00:57,125
It's very important.

978
01:00:58,417 --> 01:01:00,834
This is the fashion. That is the fashion.

979
01:01:01,250 --> 01:01:06,333
And all these fashions are extremely, extremely destructive.

980
01:01:06,583 --> 01:01:09,333
Now, not to put oil in the hair

981
01:01:10,542 --> 01:01:13,208
and end up with bald heads. All right.

982
01:01:13,542 --> 01:01:15,542
Then there are specialists, you see,

983
01:01:15,542 --> 01:01:19,583
again designers who make wigs, designer's wig.

984
01:01:19,834 --> 01:01:23,125
So you carry a wig on your head and write it down, 'designer's.'

985
01:01:28,208 --> 01:01:30,333
My idea is to see

986
01:01:30,792 --> 01:01:36,250
how stupid human beings can become with their intellect.

987
01:01:38,250 --> 01:01:42,999
Today I don't want to describe the qualities of Shri Krishna

988
01:01:42,999 --> 01:01:45,125
because you know them.

989
01:01:46,208 --> 01:01:49,125
But how you people have gone away,

990
01:01:49,583 --> 01:01:55,083
in the West, from Shri Krishna's styles,

991
01:01:55,333 --> 01:01:57,125
His methods.

992
01:01:57,709 --> 01:02:00,709
Whatever He did was to destroy the evil,

993
01:02:01,417 --> 01:02:03,875
to destroy the negativity

994
01:02:04,208 --> 01:02:06,917
and to bring forth the joy,

995
01:02:07,542 --> 01:02:11,999
which is Ras, He started. "Ras" - Ra is energy with that.

996
01:02:12,583 --> 01:02:15,125
The Ras is the energy,

997
01:02:15,458 --> 01:02:18,999
which you have

998
01:02:19,583 --> 01:02:22,709
and that's how you play the Ras,

999
01:02:22,999 --> 01:02:24,917
with that energy and enjoy.

1000
01:02:25,125 --> 01:02:26,583
He brought it Holi.

1001
01:02:26,583 --> 01:02:28,542
Of course now "Holi" can be anything,

1002
01:02:28,792 --> 01:02:34,417
but very sensible Holy he brought just to express your joy

1003
01:02:34,667 --> 01:02:37,083
in mirthful, playful ways,

1004
01:02:37,458 --> 01:02:41,125
because that was lacking in Shri Rama's life.

1005
01:02:41,125 --> 01:02:44,917
So He said just allow yourself to enjoy,

1006
01:02:44,917 --> 01:02:49,250
but this was only for Sahaja Yogis.

1007
01:02:49,999 --> 01:02:51,583
Not for others.

1008
01:02:51,583 --> 01:02:55,834
Others, you know that they go to the pubs

1009
01:02:55,834 --> 01:02:58,667
and what happens. We have a certificate here that

1010
01:02:58,667 --> 01:03:02,583
we are very peaceful, very good people, this and that.

1011
01:03:02,875 --> 01:03:05,417
This is what Shri Krishna said

1012
01:03:05,875 --> 01:03:07,417
and has done,

1013
01:03:07,875 --> 01:03:10,709
that we have to enjoy everything,

1014
01:03:11,041 --> 01:03:13,417
but in a dharmic way.

1015
01:03:14,291 --> 01:03:16,291
We should not be adharmic.

1016
01:03:17,166 --> 01:03:19,625
The Dharma should give you Joy.

1017
01:03:19,875 --> 01:03:22,417
Otherwise, if you are dharmic, you know what happens,

1018
01:03:22,709 --> 01:03:25,041
that you become absolutely austere,

1019
01:03:27,417 --> 01:03:29,542
person, joyless person

1020
01:03:30,250 --> 01:03:34,542
and sometimes cynical

1021
01:03:35,083 --> 01:03:37,750
because you think others are adharmic and this and that.

1022
01:03:38,291 --> 01:03:41,875
But Shri Krishna's ways were that you should be mirthful,

1023
01:03:41,875 --> 01:03:43,542
you should be joyful

1024
01:03:43,542 --> 01:03:46,875
and this joy will communicate with others.

1025
01:03:49,750 --> 01:03:53,959
Without this joyous nature you cannot be communicator.

1026
01:03:54,625 --> 01:03:56,750
But, as you know, when I went to French,

1027
01:03:57,041 --> 01:03:58,834
they told Me, "Mother, you look so joyous,

1028
01:03:59,041 --> 01:04:00,875
you should tell you are miserable."

1029
01:04:01,083 --> 01:04:02,667
I said, "But I am not."

1030
01:04:02,667 --> 01:04:04,999
"If you don't tell, then they won't believe you."

1031
01:04:05,208 --> 01:04:07,083
I said, "Why?" "Because they are all miserable

1032
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:10,500
and they think they are very unhappy people."

1033
01:04:11,291 --> 01:04:14,625
So I started my lecture with "Les Miserables"

1034
01:04:15,083 --> 01:04:19,625
and I told them that at every fourth lamppost

1035
01:04:20,041 --> 01:04:24,375
you find a prostitute and every tenth one a pub.

1036
01:04:25,542 --> 01:04:30,375
And I see so many people sitting on the pavement,

1037
01:04:30,625 --> 01:04:32,834
so I asked them, "Why are they sitting here?"

1038
01:04:32,834 --> 01:04:35,041
Said, "They are waiting the whole world to be destroyed."

1039
01:04:35,041 --> 01:04:38,959
I said, "Really?" After drinking, these ideas come in,

1040
01:04:39,166 --> 01:04:40,792
that let the whole world be destroyed

1041
01:04:40,792 --> 01:04:43,875
because maybe they don't have any more money to go to pubs.

1042
01:04:43,875 --> 01:04:45,625
I don't know why.

1043
01:04:47,041 --> 01:04:49,500
Now, think their level,

1044
01:04:49,999 --> 01:04:52,166
just think of their level.

1045
01:04:52,959 --> 01:04:54,500
Where are they

1046
01:04:56,959 --> 01:04:58,500
compared to you all?

1047
01:04:59,417 --> 01:05:03,959
So He's the one, as Virata,

1048
01:05:04,166 --> 01:05:06,417
puts light into your brain.

