1050
01:05:12,208 --> 01:05:13,959
what is unwise.

1051
01:05:14,333 --> 01:05:17,041
This is the blessing of Shri Krishna.

1052
01:05:18,667 --> 01:05:23,750
And He gives you the nirananda

1053
01:05:24,041 --> 01:05:27,959
because if you don't have the light you cannot enjoy

1054
01:05:29,417 --> 01:05:33,792
the joy of your mind

1055
01:05:34,083 --> 01:05:36,333
or the joy of your brain.

1056
01:05:36,667 --> 01:05:37,959
You cannot.

1057
01:05:38,875 --> 01:05:42,208
And it is through His light

1058
01:05:42,792 --> 01:05:44,417
that we see

1059
01:05:46,417 --> 01:05:51,417
ourselves as something full of joy

1060
01:05:51,417 --> 01:05:53,999
and we don't know what to do with it

