1116
01:08:58,875 --> 01:09:01,333
At least if you Sahaja Yogis keep your Vishuddhi all right,

1117
01:09:01,625 --> 01:09:03,667
I'll be much better off.

1118
01:09:04,083 --> 01:09:06,875
