1262
01:17:00,999 --> 01:17:03,500
What is the main thing of your life?

1263
01:17:04,375 --> 01:17:08,083
And I was surprised how people are lost in the music.

1264
01:17:09,999 --> 01:17:12,959
I mean there should be some occasion.

1265
01:17:13,959 --> 01:17:17,999
They're all already in another world with the music.

1266
01:17:18,834 --> 01:17:20,166
Don't do these things.

1267
01:17:20,417 --> 01:17:22,959
You go to extremes of everything.

1268
01:17:23,250 --> 01:17:25,667
That's not proper, even pujas, anything,

1269
01:17:25,667 --> 01:17:27,375
you go to extremes.

1270
01:17:27,375 --> 01:17:29,999
To go to extremes, you won't be in the center.

1271
01:17:30,375 --> 01:17:34,875
You will not be in the place of Shri Krishna,

1272
01:17:35,166 --> 01:17:37,250
where you have to be.

1273
01:17:37,542 --> 01:17:39,709
On the contrary, you will be

1274
01:17:40,500 --> 01:17:43,375
just in another imaginary world.

1275
01:17:45,291 --> 01:17:50,959
So, as a matter of habit we create a world like that;

1276
01:17:51,166 --> 01:17:52,500
somebody has music world;

1277
01:17:52,500 --> 01:17:54,250
somebody has dancing world;

1278
01:17:54,500 --> 01:17:56,083
another one has,

