01:17:58,875 --> 01:18:02,417
world, I've seen with Sahaja Yogis who think

1280
01:18:02,834 --> 01:18:04,625
no end of themselves.

1281
01:18:04,875 --> 01:18:07,291
"We have a special relationship with Shri Mataji."

1282
01:18:07,291 --> 01:18:08,959
Is a very common thing.

1283
01:18:09,166 --> 01:18:11,959
But I cannot have any special relationship.

1284
01:18:13,083 --> 01:18:14,166
Sorry,

1285
01:18:17,166 --> 01:18:20,834
nobody has any special relationship with Me.

1286
01:18:21,291 --> 01:18:24,166
This I would like to tell you very clearly,

1287
01:18:24,750 --> 01:18:26,709
and you should not claim that,

1288
01:18:27,083 --> 01:18:29,417
